| HC/MHC | 用 PyTorch fallback 表达 hyper-connection 语义，延迟敏感执行链路使用 TileLang/MUSA native 实现 | `python/sglang/srt/models/deepseek_v4.py`、`python/sglang/srt/layers/mhc*` | `flatten`、`float`、`square`、`mean`、`rsqrt`、`F.linear`、`sum`、`contiguous` |
